  "3251170": {
    "name": "Lirai: Heir Of Darkness",
    "steam_appid": 3251170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/24c3d2441684d56eb3ab56418f6462e4.avif?t=1768528194\" width=1344 height=525 /></span>Lirai: Heir Of Darkness 是一款以末世为背景的惊险刺激的第三人称动作游戏。曾经充满生机的地球现在到处都是危险的敌人--僵尸、恶魔、巨型怪物和顽强的人类幸存者--大家都在争夺统治权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/c6031216aca040405b84f58e273e35d2.poster.avif?t=1768528194\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/c6031216aca040405b84f58e273e35d2.webm?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/c6031216aca040405b84f58e273e35d2.mp4?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏给人一种紧张的感觉，环境多变，人物关系复杂。故事情节揭示了导致世界崩溃的黑暗秘密。玩家将在这个危险的世界中穿梭，利用自己的战斗技能和各种策略在这个混乱的地方生存下来并揭开真相。导致毁灭和混乱的恐怖世界还剩下什么？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/1824e1a685e39bbf3f20388bc5b1674d.poster.avif?t=1768528194\" width=328 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/1824e1a685e39bbf3f20388bc5b1674d.webm?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/1824e1a685e39bbf3f20388bc5b1674d.mp4?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/3a1509b948d65c6634c6657fdfce45bf.avif?t=1768528194\" width=1344 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演的布莱恩是一名骑士，也是人类最后的希望之一。布莱恩凭借自己的技能和决心，踏上了拯救人类的伟大征程。在这个危机四伏的世界里，他的旅程将是对自己极限的考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/06f768981b7e0a93cc9cb977a503d686.avif?t=1768528194\" width=1344 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/27ce974005c14a0b247dba7f341caded.poster.avif?t=1768528194\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/27ce974005c14a0b247dba7f341caded.webm?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/27ce974005c14a0b247dba7f341caded.mp4?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>概述 Lirai》讲述的是布莱恩的旅程，他是一个被无情的世界末日蹂躏的虚假战士。众多恶魔和僵尸在地球上泛滥成灾，人类濒临被彻底消灭的边缘。无奈之下，幸存的人类联合起来，作为最后的军队对抗他们。在一片混乱中，布莱恩必须揭开秘密，确保人类的未来，同时奋力杀出一条血路。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/b3c58f17b55d9d87c5bf442cc31c40d7.poster.avif?t=1768528194\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/b3c58f17b55d9d87c5bf442cc31c40d7.webm?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/b3c58f17b55d9d87c5bf442cc31c40d7.mp4?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/62c4f67a763fa7037d9eff159043a074.avif?t=1768528194\" width=1344 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“拯救世界已不再是个人的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类必须夺回失去的一切。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 《幸存者编年史》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/209e0391d8ec2938eca9bab080ddc8ef.avif?t=1768528194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras_big/209e0391d8ec2938eca9bab080ddc8ef.avif?t=1768528194 width=800 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接激烈的战斗、策略性的游戏和扣人心弦的故事吧，它们会让你坐立不安。人类的未来掌握在您的手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/9bae4b5ebd416e5bd3374688d9934efb.poster.avif?t=1768528194\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/9bae4b5ebd416e5bd3374688d9934efb.webm?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251170/extras/9bae4b5ebd416e5bd3374688d9934efb.mp4?t=1768528194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作紧张的剑术战斗。与各种敌人进行快节奏的战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lirai》的叙事重点是人物之间的复杂关系以及导致末日混乱的故事。通过故事和人物，揭开衰落背后的神秘面纱。情感深度和人物成长是故事的核心。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种可玩变身--每种变身都有独特的能力和外观。这些变身具有不同的游戏机制和策略。每种形态都会带来不同的玩法。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lirai》中的每个关卡都有自己的谜团和谜题，旨在鼓励玩家进行探索和批判性思考。玩家需要通过复杂的谜题，揭开隐藏的秘密，解开故事的谜团。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与布莱恩一起踏上旅程，通过故事和游戏中的发现进行探索，以拯救人类免于憎恶和灭绝。</p></li></ul>",
